# PropAgent Design System

## Colors (ONLY these)
- Primary: `#2563EB`
- Dark/Sidebar: `#0F172A`
- Background: `#F8FAFC`
- Surface/Cards: `#FFFFFF`
- Muted text: `#64748B`
- Success: `#16A34A`
- Warning: `#D97706`
- Danger: `#DC2626`
- Border: `rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08)`

No neon, no random gradients, no crypto-style UI.

## Typography
- Font: Inter (via next/font)
- No emoji icons — Lucide React only

## Layout
- Border radius: cards 16–24px, buttons 8–18px
- Spacing: 8pt grid (8/16/24/32/40/48px)
- Touch targets: minimum 44×44px on mobile
- Mobile-first responsive design

## Required UI States
Every data-fetching component MUST have:
1. Loading skeleton (never blank screen)
2. Empty state with actionable CTA
3. Error state with retry button

## Frontend Patterns
- API calls via `lib/api.ts` — never raw fetch scattered in components
- Realtime via `hooks/useRealtime.ts` (Socket.IO)
- No external UI libraries — Tailwind only unless explicitly approved
- Dashboard auth via JWT stored securely (httpOnly cookie when implemented)

## Page Limits
- Max 1 primary chart per analytics page
- Bottom nav max 3 tabs on mobile dashboard
- Primary CTA max 1 per section
